snippet.title: Picnic Penguin Launch Trailer
snippet.description: As a fan of both penguins and alliteration, I was quickly drawn to Picnic Penguin. This cute puzzler is all about helping the penguin push tasty treats onto the picnic blanket. http://neutronized.com/PicnicPenguin/index.php
